      "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
      "Text": "The development of frost and heat damage functions was supported by the ‘Frost and Heat Management Analytics’ (FAHMA) project via funding from the Grains Research and Development Corporation (GRDC; Grant No. CSP2204-009RTX).",
