                {
                  "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                  "Text": "Cultivar names include several codes for several traits.\n* RR = Roundup Ready - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance for Glyphosate herbicide.\n* CL = Clearfield - These cultivars as developed for the Clearfield Canola weed control system.\n* TT = Triazine Tolerant - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance for triazine herbicide\n* RT = Triazine and Roundup - These cultivars are developed to provide tolerance to both triazine and glyphosate herbicides.",
                  "Name": "Memo",
                  "ResourceName": null,
                  "Children": [],
                  "Enabled": true,
